title: Jing Jing
typeOfFood: Chinese, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Cambodian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Situated along the Sangke River in the city center with a river view and surrounded by open-air eateries and stalls selling a variety of local wares, shops, restaurants. For vegetarians there are stir-fried noodles with in-season local vegetables and also fried rice with your choice of ingredients. Water, soft-drinks, and beer. Food is prepared, cooked and served by family members.
streetAddress: Road 1, Preak Moha Tep Village, Sangkat Suay Por
